The,Red,Hat,OpenShift,API,gives,developers,a,platform,in,the,cloud,to,build,test,deploy,and,run,applications,The,API,receives,RESTful,calls,and,send,callbacks,in,JSON,and,XML,Calls,require,basic,HTTP,Authentication,in,the,form,of,a,user,name,and,password,generated,upon,sign,up,Applications,can,be,built,using,Ruby,Python,and,PHP